description: Wraps the parameters to execute a resequencing of elements containing a sequence_no field.
title: ResequenceCommand

uri.description: The URI of the configuration entity

start_sequence_value.description: Starting value of the sequence_no For policy resequence command, max_value is 2147483646

incremental_sequence_value.description: Incremental value of the sequence_no For policy resequence command, max_value is 2147483645

acl_id.description: ACL ID of the rules to resequence. One of acl_id/traffic_class_id/policy_id is mandatory. acl_id is mandatory for ACL resequence command.

traffic_class_id.description: QoS Traffic Class ID of the matches to resequence. One of acl_id/traffic_class_id/policy_id is mandatory. traffic_class_id is mandatory for qos traffic class resequence command.

policy_id.description: QoS Policy ID of the actions to resequence. One of acl_id/traffic_class_id/policy_id is mandatory. policy_id is mandatory for qos policy resequence command.
